Package: Rcomments
Type: Package
Title: Commenting Addin using GPT-3.5
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("LazaR", "K", email = "lkovacevic360@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Rcomments is an RStudio addin that utilizes the GPT-3.5 Turbo API to automatically add comments to selected lines of R code. It provides concise explanations for each line of code and suggests next steps for further analysis. This tool enhances the code documentation process, making it easier for users to understand and extend their R scripts. Ideal for both beginners and advanced users, Rcomments streamlines code annotation and analysis planning within the RStudio environment.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    rstudioapi,
    httr
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
URL: https://github.com/lazaR360K/Rcomments
BugReports: https://github.com/lazaR360K/Rcomments/issues
